Fri Jan  9 22:25:53 UTC 2026 - Marius Grossu <marius.grossu@suse.com>

- Update to 2.5:
  * The wait() helper has become an official part of the python-copr API
  * Copr now allows storing wildcard strings in the "Packit allowed forge projects" field
  * The Fedora Copr Frontend is now protected by Anubis to defend against unreasonable bot load
- complete changelog:
  * https://github.com/fedora-copr/copr/compare/python-copr-2.1-1...python-copr-2.5-1

